1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,740
Urgent question dies

2
00:00:01,740 --> 00:00:03,280
in silence.

3
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:04,280
Someone typed into

4
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:05,280
your website —

5
00:00:05,280 --> 00:00:06,300
during business hours

6
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:07,300
— and got

7
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:08,300
nothing back.

8
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:09,560
Not after midnight.

9
00:00:09,560 --> 00:00:11,000
Not on a holiday.

10
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:12,580
Tuesday afternoon.

11
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:14,340
You were technically open.

12
00:00:14,340 --> 00:00:15,340
Your website just

13
00:00:15,340 --> 00:00:16,900
couldn't say a word.

14
00:00:16,900 --> 00:00:18,140
They waited maybe

15
00:00:18,140 --> 00:00:19,140
thirty seconds.

16
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:20,140
Then they moved on.

17
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:21,140
And you never

18
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:22,480
saw it happen.

19
00:00:22,480 --> 00:00:23,760
Every day,

20
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,700
qualified visitors land,

21
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:26,800
ask nothing,

22
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:27,820
leave everything.

23
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:28,960
Your site looks complete.

24
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,180
It just can't

25
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:31,800
hold a conversation.

26
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:32,800
That's the gap

27
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,800
nobody talks about.
